1.0 (no_unix)
* remove dependency on the Unix module
* added set_timestamp_fun
* added get_timestamp_fun
* the default timestamp_fun is Sys.time
1.0.0
* removed logging statements taking a lazy string as a parameter
* simpler log function
* updated copyright
* corrected ocamldoc
0.6.0
* exposed string_of_level
* added level_of_string
0.5.0
* Make printf-like functions lazy
* more tests
0.3.0 (trunk)
* Clean the build system
* Expose `Log.log` to the user
* Add a functorial interface to handle sections
* Add printf-like functions
